com.ihealth.communication.control

Interface AmProfile


  • public interface AmProfile
    Public APIs for the AM serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager.registerClientCallback(com.ihealth.communication.manager.iHealthDevicesCallback) register. When new data from AM device, The Callback{#iHealthDevicesCallback #onDeviceNotify} can be triggered should call.
